    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, I'm confused. Why did you mention goblins and wizards? I'm just a graphic designer trying to understand a legal document, not playing a game. \n\nCan you please ignore the metaphors and just give me a serious, professional explanation? I specifically need to know if this clause means I could be sued personally for more than just the cost of my contract if something goes wrong.",
